lete|[[Philippe Thys]]|BEL}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1914 Tour de France, Stage 9 to Stage 15#Stage 10|10]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 16 July || [[Nice]] to [[Grenoble]]\n| {{convert|323|km|mi|abbr=on}} || [[File:Mountainstage.svg|20px|alt=|link=]] || Stage with mountain(s)|| {{flagathlete|[[Henri P\u00e9lissier]]|FRA}} || {{flagathlete|[[Philippe Thys]]|BEL}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1914 Tour de France, Stage 9 to Stage 15#Stage 11|11]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 18 July || [[Grenoble]] to [[Geneva]]\n| {{convert|325|km|mi|abbr=on}} || [[File:Mountainstage.svg|20px|alt=|link=]] || Stage with mountain(s)|| {{flagathlete|[[Gustave Garrigou]]|FRA}} || {{flagathlete|[[Philippe Thys]]|BEL}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1914 Tour de France, Stage 9 to Stage 15#Stage 12|12]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 20 July || [[Geneva]] to [[Belfort]]\n| {{convert|325|km|mi|abbr=on}} || [[File:Mountainstage.svg|20px|alt=|link=]] || Stage with mountain(s)|| {{flagathlete|[[Henri P\u00e9lissier]]|FRA}} || {{flagathlete|[[Philippe Thys]]|BEL}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1914 Tour de France, Stage 9 to Stage 15#Stage 13|13]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 22 July || [[Belfort]] to [[Longwy]]\n| {{convert|325|km|mi|abbr=on}} || [[File:Mountainstage.svg|20px|alt=|link=]] || Stage with mountain(s)|| {{flagathlete|[[Fran\u00e7ois Faber]]|LUX}} || {{flagathlete|[[Philippe Thys]]|BEL}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1914 Tour de France, Stage 9 to Stage 15#Stage 14|14]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 24 July || [[Longwy]] to [[Dunkerque]]\n| {{convert|390|km|mi|abbr=on}} || [[File:Plainstage.svg|20px|alt=|link=]] || Plain stage|| {{flagathlete|[[Fran\u00e7ois Faber]]|LUX}} || {{flagathlete|[[Philippe Thys]]|BEL}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[1914 Tour de France, Stage 9 to Stage 15#Stage 15|15]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 26 July || [[Dunkerque]] to [[Paris]]\n| {{convert|340|km|mi|abbr=on}} || [[File:Plainstage.svg|20px|alt=|link=]] || Plain stage|| {{flagathlete|[[Henri P\